### Additional API Examples for Coach and Match Controllers

### COACH ENDPOINTS

### 1. Get all coaches
GET http://localhost:8080/api/coaches
Accept: application/json

### 2. Get coach by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/coaches/1
Accept: application/json

### 3. Get coach by name
GET http://localhost:8080/api/coaches/name/Pep Guardiola
Accept: application/json

### 4. Get coaches by nationality
GET http://localhost:8080/api/coaches/nationality/Spanish
Accept: application/json

### 5. Get coaches by minimum experience
GET http://localhost:8080/api/coaches/experience/10
Accept: application/json

### 6. Get coaches by age range
GET http://localhost:8080/api/coaches/age-range?minAge=40&maxAge=60
Accept: application/json

### 7. Get available coaches (without teams)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/coaches/available
Accept: application/json

### 8. Get coaches with teams
GET http://localhost:8080/api/coaches/with-teams
Accept: application/json

### 9. Create new coach
POST http://localhost:8080/api/coaches
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Mikel Arteta",
  "age": 41,
  "nationality": "Spanish",
  "experienceYears": 4
}

### 10. Update coach
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/coaches/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Pep Guardiola",
  "age": 53,
  "nationality": "Spanish",
  "experienceYears": 16
}

### 11. Delete coach
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/coaches/5

### 12. Check if coach exists
GET http://localhost:8080/api/coaches/1/exists
Accept: application/json

### MATCH ENDPOINTS

### 13. Get all matches
GET http://localhost:8080/api/matches
Accept: application/json

### 14. Get match by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/matches/1
Accept: application/json

### 15. Get matches by league
GET http://localhost:8080/api/matches/league/1
Accept: application/json

### 16. Get matches by status
GET http://localhost:8080/api/matches/status/FINISHED
Accept: application/json

### 17. Get matches by round
GET http://localhost:8080/api/matches/round/1
Accept: application/json

### 18. Get matches by team
GET http://localhost:8080/api/matches/team/1
Accept: application/json

### 19. Get home matches by team
GET http://localhost:8080/api/matches/team/1/home
Accept: application/json

### 20. Get away matches by team
GET http://localhost:8080/api/matches/team/1/away
Accept: application/json

### 21. Get matches by date range
GET http://localhost:8080/api/matches/date-range?startDate=2024-01-01T00:00:00&endDate=2024-12-31T23:59:59
Accept: application/json

### 22. Get matches by league and round
GET http://localhost:8080/api/matches/league/1/round/1
Accept: application/json

### 23. Get matches between two teams
GET http://localhost:8080/api/matches/between-teams?team1Id=1&team2Id=2
Accept: application/json

### 24. Create new match
POST http://localhost:8080/api/matches
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "matchDate": "2024-12-15T15:00:00",
  "homeTeamId": 1,
  "awayTeamId": 2,
  "leagueId": 1,
  "round": 2,
  "status": "SCHEDULED"
}

### 25. Update match (finish match with score)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/matches/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "matchDate": "2024-12-01T15:00:00",
  "homeTeamId": 1,
  "awayTeamId": 2,
  "leagueId": 1,
  "round": 1,
  "status": "FINISHED",
  "homeTeamScore": 3,
  "awayTeamScore": 1
}

### 26. Create friendly match (without league)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/matches
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "matchDate": "2024-12-20T18:00:00",
  "homeTeamId": 1,
  "awayTeamId": 3,
  "round": 1,
  "status": "SCHEDULED"
}

### 27. Delete match
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/matches/3

### 28. Check if match exists
GET http://localhost:8080/api/matches/1/exists
Accept: application/json

### COMPLEX SCENARIOS

### 29. Create coach and assign to team
POST http://localhost:8080/api/coaches
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Antonio Conte",
  "age": 54,
  "nationality": "Italian",
  "experienceYears": 12
}

### 30. Update team with new coach
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/teams/5
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Arsenal",
  "city": "London",
  "foundedYear": 1886,
  "stadium": "Emirates Stadium",
  "leagueId": 1,
  "coachId": 5
}

### 31. Create match between teams from different leagues
POST http://localhost:8080/api/matches
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "matchDate": "2024-12-25T20:00:00",
  "homeTeamId": 1,
  "awayTeamId": 3,
  "round": 1,
  "status": "SCHEDULED"
}
